    a546e36bf0527c9d3b16154b82465edd62144c0ac1fc5a18506a2244ba449ac4
  Input u-coordinate (peer public):
    e6db6867583030db3594c1a424b15f7c726624ec26b3353b10a903a6d0ab1c4c
